OL,3,CIsle of Wight man bringing joy to his
OL,4,Ccommunity whilst fundraising for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FChristopher Hayton has made it his
OL,8,Fmission to raise awareness about
OL,9,Fmental health conditions, and bring a
OL,10,Flittle joy and colour to his community
OL,11,Fat the same time.
OL,13,FHe has raised thousands for a charity
OL,14,Fvery dear to his heart through the
OL,15,Fgarden troughs he makes from discarded
OL,16,Fwooden palettes.
OL,18,FChristopher from Ryde on the Isle of
OL,19,FWight has built and given away
OL,20,Fhundreds of the planters, which can be
OL,21,Ffilled with colourful flowers.
