OL,3,CIsle of Wight man bringing joy to his
OL,4,Ccommunity whilst fundraising for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"I've been struggling with depression,
OL,8,Fanxiety and stress for the last 40
OL,9,Fyears," Christopher said.
OL,11,F"But at the same time I am feeling
OL,12,Fhappy now that I am helping people out.
OL,14,F"It stops you feeling depressed when
OL,15,Fyou've got something positive on your
OL,16,Fmind."
OL,18,FSo far he's constructed 1,753 garden
OL,19,Ftroughs, and residents can make a
OL,20,Fdonation to the Samaritans.
