OL,7,FThe planters can be found in many
OL,8,Fpublic and private spaces around Ryde-
OL,9,F giving a boost to his friends and
OL,10,Fneighbours' garden walls.
OL,12,FNeighbour Cynthia Brodie said: "It
OL,13,Fbrings brightness to my day, because I
OL,14,Flove colour. I love flowers and I like
OL,15,Fpeople to say ooh isn't it beautiful.
OL,17,F"He's created all these plant troughs
OL,18,Fand he hasn't done it for himself.
OL,20,F"He's a giver and I am so proud of
OL,21,Fhim."
