OL,7,F"Chris has overcome some of his own
OL,8,Fdifficulties in life.
OL,10,F"I think what's really impressive
OL,11,Fabout Chris is the way he has done
OL,12,Fthat and carries on and goes out every
OL,13,Fday and does what he does for the
OL,14,Fcommunity."
